snippet.title: FANTASIAN Neo Dimension - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
The Father of FINAL FANTASY, Hironobu Sakaguchi, and renowned composer Nobuo Uematsu return to deliver an original RPG story.

Embark on an multi-dimensional journey to reclaim your lost memories and save the world from the mechteria infection. 

FANTASIAN Neo Dimension launches on Nintendo Switch, PlayStation 5, PlayStation 4, Steam, and Xbox Series X|S this Winter 2024. 

Follow us for all the latest on FANTASIAN Neo Dimension:
Website: https://www.FantasianNeoDimension.com/
X: https://www.twitter.com/Fantasian_EN
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/SquareEnix
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/SquareEnix
